Distribution. This species is widely distributed in the Western Pacific islands, including the Ryukyus (e.g., Ishigaki and Iriomote islands), Taiwan , Guam , the Philippines , Sulawesi, Papua New Guinea , and Vanuatu . In Taiwan , this species is found from northern (Magang, Taipei County), eastern (Ilan and Taitung), southern (Pingtung), and southwestern parts (Tainan City) of the main island; and the offshore Penghu Islands (Pescadores) in the Taiwan Strait (
Fig. 1
).
